    "# Retrieval Augmented Generation (RAG) with LlamaIndex\n",
    "*Using IBM Granite Models*"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {
    "jupyter": {
     "outputs_hidden": false
    },
    "pycharm": {
     "name": "#%% md\n"
    }
